  "text": "\u03c8 1 and \u03c8 3 are the amplitudes describing no spin flip, \u03c8 5 -single flip, \u03c8 2 and \u03c8 4 -double flip. These amplitudes can be calculated using a vertex (\u0393) and a propagator (\u2206) functions, specific for each Pomeron spin (cf. [CITATION_1] ):",
